ResBlock

Source: R/blocks.R
ResBlock.Rd

Resnet block from `ni` to `nh` with `stride`

ResBlock(
  expansion,
  ni,
  nf,
  stride = 1,
  groups = 1,
  reduction = NULL,
  nh1 = NULL,
  nh2 = NULL,
  dw = FALSE,
  g2 = 1,
  sa = FALSE,
  sym = FALSE,
  norm_type = 1,
  act_cls = nn$ReLU,
  ndim = 2,
  ks = 3,
  pool = AvgPool(),
  pool_first = TRUE,
  padding = NULL,
  bias = NULL,
  bn_1st = TRUE,
  transpose = FALSE,
  init = "auto",
  xtra = NULL,
  bias_std = 0.01,
  dilation = 1,
  padding_mode = "zeros"
)
